1463
01:34:51,290 --> 01:34:52,290
I see.

1464
01:34:52,560 --> 01:34:53,690
It was exactly the same.

1465
01:34:54,490 --> 01:34:57,500
You used the most luxurious ingredients...

1466
01:34:57,730 --> 01:34:59,700
