1467
01:34:59,900 --> 01:35:01,846
but it's a little disappointing because it was predictable.

1468
01:35:01,870 --> 01:35:04,070
Still, I enjoyed your dish very much. Thank you.

1469
01:35:04,470 --> 01:35:07,190
I was a little upset to hear that, but I was satisfied with my dish.

1470
01:35:07,470 --> 01:35:09,980
So I just accepted his feedback.

1471
01:35:15,610 --> 01:35:17,779
All evaluations for Part One...

1472
01:35:17,780 --> 01:35:20,090
