1481
01:36:06,670 --> 01:36:09,170
And Rank 7's total score is 505.

1482
01:36:09,700 --> 01:36:12,870
The highest and lowest scores are 51 points apart.

1483
01:36:14,770 --> 01:36:15,810
Fifty-one points.

1484
01:36:16,210 --> 01:36:18,009
I must be in first place.

1485
01:36:18,010 --> 01:36:20,850
I thought that would get me an advantage.

1486
01:36:20,950 --> 01:36:22,449
I wanted to be in first place.

1487
01:36:22,450 --> 01:36:25,449
To go to Part Two with that total score?

1488
01:36:25,450 --> 01:36:27,420
It'll be a huge advantage.

1489
01:36:27,920 --> 01:36:29,489
If I am in first place,

1490
01:36:29,490 --> 01:36:32,389
