1491
01:36:32,390 --> 01:36:34,789
I saw that Rank 1 and Rank 7's scores were quite different.

1492
01:36:34,790 --> 01:36:37,559
But from Rank 4 to Rank 1,

1493
01:36:37,560 --> 01:36:39,730
