1494
01:36:58,150 --> 01:37:01,720
We'll begin with Rank Seven.

1495
01:37:02,020 --> 01:37:03,060
We start with Rank Seven?

1496
01:37:03,560 --> 01:37:05,790
Rank Seven does have a big difference from the others.

1497
01:37:08,030 --> 01:37:10,730
A total score of 505.

1498
01:37:11,960 --> 01:37:14,630
Who is the contender to rank seventh?

1499
01:37:16,940 --> 01:37:17,940
