1501
01:37:22,940 --> 01:37:26,480
Prince of Cannoli, Contender Seong Min Su.

1502
01:37:33,920 --> 01:37:37,659
Unfortunately, you received the lowest score in Part One.

1503
01:37:37,660 --> 01:37:39,589
How are you feeling?

1504
01:37:39,590 --> 01:37:40,790
Honestly,

1505
01:37:41,030 --> 01:37:43,459
I expected myself to be in last place.

1506
01:37:43,460 --> 01:37:45,160
Everyone else was just so good.

1507
01:37:46,070 --> 01:37:48,230
I can't say I was surprised.

1508
01:37:48,530 --> 01:37:50,340
But seven is a lucky number,

1509
01:37:51,070 --> 01:37:52,939
