1510
01:37:52,940 --> 01:37:54,039
There you go.

1511
01:37:54,040 --> 01:37:57,480
I'll do my very best for Part Two of the final round.

1512
01:37:57,880 --> 01:37:59,280
You can do this!

1513
01:37:59,910 --> 01:38:01,809
- You never know until the end. - Let's go!

1514
01:38:01,810 --> 01:38:03,750
Next, Rank Six.

1515
01:38:04,750 --> 01:38:06,490
A total score of 520.

1516
01:38:07,150 --> 01:38:09,420
Rank Six goes to...

1517
01:38:16,300 --> 01:38:20,130
Bakery on Top of Mount Bukhan, Contender Kim Jin Seo.

1518
01:38:32,980 --> 01:38:34,650
I'm 36 points away from 1st place.

1519
01:38:37,620 --> 01:38:40,320
I was angry with myself.

1520
01:38:40,520 --> 01:38:42,120
I really reflected on myself too.

1521
01:38:42,420 --> 01:38:46,259
But this didn't make me lose my confidence.

1522
01:38:46,260 --> 01:38:48,529
I'm going to prove myself...

1523
01:38:48,530 --> 01:38:49,760
