1524
01:38:50,760 --> 01:38:55,430
Next, Rank 5 with a total score of 527.

1525
01:39:01,540 --> 01:39:04,480
Baking Idol, Contender Ju Young Seok.

1526
01:39:10,880 --> 01:39:13,349
What a shame. His dish was good.

1527
01:39:13,350 --> 01:39:14,490
Yes, I enjoyed it too.

1528
01:39:16,020 --> 01:39:17,120
I was disappointed.

1529
01:39:17,560 --> 01:39:20,829
But I'm not too far behind,

1530
01:39:20,830 --> 01:39:24,300
