1534
01:39:44,820 --> 01:39:47,890
The Crazy Pastry Chef, Contender Hwang Ji Oh.

1535
01:39:55,660 --> 01:39:57,829
Rank Four is just a few points behind.

1536
01:39:57,830 --> 01:40:00,170
- She can turn it around anytime. - Definitely.

1537
01:40:00,730 --> 01:40:02,300
