1541
01:40:10,740 --> 01:40:13,150
I'm just 24 points away from Rank 1.

1542
01:40:13,350 --> 01:40:14,410
I can turn it around.

1543
01:40:14,580 --> 01:40:16,700
I want to overtake them and climb back up to the top.

1544
01:40:17,950 --> 01:40:20,820
