1545
01:40:21,050 --> 01:40:22,620
But she's Rank 4,

1546
01:40:22,890 --> 01:40:24,090
with just a few points behind.

1547
01:40:24,590 --> 01:40:28,759
We just have three contenders left.

1548
01:40:28,760 --> 01:40:30,160
Ranks 1, 2, and 3.

1549
01:40:31,860 --> 01:40:34,830
It's getting intense.

1550
01:40:34,970 --> 01:40:38,700
Ranks 2 and 3 are just 4 points apart.

1551
01:40:40,410 --> 01:40:41,870
I can't back down anymore.

1552
01:40:42,210 --> 01:40:44,340
I'm going for Rank One and nothing less.

1553
01:40:45,110 --> 01:40:47,680
My goal in Part One of the final round...

1554
01:40:47,950 --> 01:40:48,980
is to win first place.

1555
01:40:50,180 --> 01:40:52,649
I'll admit that I'm intimidated by the other two contenders.

1556
01:40:52,650 --> 01:40:55,590
But that's more reason I should win first place.

1557
01:40:56,160 --> 01:40:59,020
We'll start with Rank Three.

1558
01:40:59,460 --> 01:41:02,190
A total score of 538.

1559
01:41:02,530 --> 01:41:04,260
Rank Three goes to...

1560
01:41:14,570 --> 01:41:18,280
Fine Dining Baker, Contender Yoon Hwa Young.

1561
01:41:25,820 --> 01:41:27,290
He's just a few points behind.

1562
01:41:31,490 --> 01:41:34,590
I was disappointed, but I wasn't too far behind.

1563
01:41:34,690 --> 01:41:37,729
I'll be able to catch up to them...

1564
01:41:37,730 --> 01:41:40,330
