1565
01:41:40,700 --> 01:41:43,470
I would've been happy even if he ranked 5th or 4th,

1566
01:41:44,270 --> 01:41:45,400
but he's Rank Three.

1567
01:41:45,970 --> 01:41:47,510
I was thrilled to see the results.

1568
01:41:47,870 --> 01:41:50,110
Anything could happen in the final mission.

1569
01:41:50,240 --> 01:41:52,679
But from what I've seen today,

1570
01:41:52,680 --> 01:41:54,040
you'll win first place, Hwa Young.

1571
01:41:54,680 --> 01:41:58,950
We just have Ranks 1 and 2 left.

1572
01:41:59,080 --> 01:42:01,149
And the contenders remaining are...

1573
01:42:01,150 --> 01:42:03,459
Dessert Macho, Contender Lee Kyung Mu,

1574
01:42:03,460 --> 01:42:06,730
and Jeju Blue Ribbon Hoarder, Contender Kim Si Yeob.

1575
01:42:06,760 --> 01:42:08,729
You both must be very nervous. How are you feeling?

1576
01:42:08,730 --> 01:42:10,799
I just want to move on to the next mission,

1577
01:42:10,800 --> 01:42:12,799
bake something amazing,

1578
01:42:12,800 --> 01:42:15,400
beat all the other contenders and win this.

1579
01:42:19,840 --> 01:42:22,240
- You're so cool. - Let's go!

1580
01:42:25,340 --> 01:42:27,350
He's just so confident.

1581
01:42:27,650 --> 01:42:29,850
I feel a chill down my spine.

1582
01:42:30,950 --> 01:42:33,950
The number two has been chasing me around on this show.

1583
01:42:38,960 --> 01:42:42,160
I'll accept this fate and Rank Two...

1584
01:42:42,830 --> 01:42:45,130
and do my very best for Part Two's mission.

1585
01:42:46,400 --> 01:42:48,469
- You never know. - He's right!

1586
01:42:48,470 --> 01:42:49,899
- Even we don't know. - Yes.

1587
01:42:49,900 --> 01:42:54,170
Then, we'll start with the total score of 556,

1588
01:42:54,240 --> 01:42:58,110
Rank 1 of Part 1 of the final round.

1589
01:43:06,350 --> 01:43:08,420
Contender Lee Kyung Mu.

1590
01:43:08,920 --> 01:43:10,560
Could you move to the next seat, please?

1591
01:43:19,130 --> 01:43:21,210
I wanted to make a place where my mother could rest,

1592
01:43:22,030 --> 01:43:25,440
somewhere she could take a breath while working.

1593
01:43:32,080 --> 01:43:36,149
I imagined my mother resting on this giant rock.

1594
01:43:36,150 --> 01:43:38,110
I want her to relax and take care of herself now.

1595
01:43:40,250 --> 01:43:42,520
A total score of 556.

1596
01:43:43,220 --> 01:43:46,330
Who will be the one to become Rank One?

1597
01:43:47,030 --> 01:43:50,600
Rank 1 in Part 1 of the final round goes to...

1598
01:43:57,670 --> 01:44:01,740
You've all worked through countless nights tirelessly.

1599
01:44:01,940 --> 01:44:03,879
It's time to see...

1600
01:44:03,880 --> 01:44:06,610
how your hard work has paid off.

1601
01:44:07,510 --> 01:44:09,179
Bake Your Dream.

1602
01:44:09,180 --> 01:44:10,450
The final competition.

1603
01:44:12,080 --> 01:44:13,389
The very last mission.

1604
01:44:13,390 --> 01:44:14,990
Part Two of the final round.

1605
01:44:18,460 --> 01:44:19,789
I'll put everything on the line...

1606
01:44:19,790 --> 01:44:21,690
and give it my all.

1607
01:44:22,190 --> 01:44:23,660
I have to win this.

1608
01:44:24,460 --> 01:44:26,970
(A chance to turn the tables)

1609
01:44:28,000 --> 01:44:29,569
I'll turn things around...

1610
01:44:29,570 --> 01:44:30,600
no matter what.

1611
01:44:31,100 --> 01:44:32,840
I'm not going to step down without a fight.

1612
01:44:32,870 --> 01:44:34,870
This competition has transformed me...

1613
01:44:35,470 --> 01:44:36,680
into a monster.

1614
01:44:40,480 --> 01:44:43,150
The final winner of Bake Your Dream is...
